* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/bɹat/}}, {{X-SAMPA|/br\{t/}}
* {{a|US}} {{enPR|brăt}}, {{IPA|/bɻæt/}}, {{X-SAMPA|/"br\`{t/}}
* {{rhymes|æt}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# A [[child]] (as a [[pejorative]] term); offspring.
#: {{usex|Get that little '''brat''' away from me!|lang=en}}
# Now often specifically, a [[selfish]] or [[spoil]]ed [[child]].
# {{context|obsolete|UK|Scotland|dialect|lang=en}} A coarse kind of [[apron]] for keeping the clothes clean; a [[bib]].
#: {{rfquotek|Wright}}
